{"id":"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations","title":"provideNoopAnimations","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/platform-browser\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/platform-browser/animations\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser/animations\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations\", \"name\": \"provideNoopAnimations\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-browser\">@angular/platform-browser</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations\">@angular/platform-browser/animations</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/platform-browser/animations/src/module.ts#L100-L126\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"providenoopanimations\">provideNoopAnimations<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations#providenoopanimations\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9hsonjw7lx0ld8rk17ohiu8nk\">返回一组<a href=\"guide/glossary#provider\">依赖注入提供程序</a>以禁用应用程序中的动画。请参阅<a href=\"guide/animations\">动画指南</a>以了解有关 Angular 中动画的更多信息。</p>\n\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideNoopAnimations</a></span>(): <a href=\"api/core/Provider\" class=\"code-anchor\">Provider</a>[]</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">参数</h6>\n  <p>没有参数。</p>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/core/Provider\" class=\"code-anchor\">Provider</a>[]</code></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9zz7gxgiah0a6m8ptj4lqebb\">当你想使用 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> 函数引导应用程序时，该函数很有用，但你需要禁用动画（例如，在运行测试时）。</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(RootComponent, {\n  providers: [\n    <a href=\"api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideNoopAnimations</a>()\n  ]\n});\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-browser/animations\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/Provider\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/animations\n - api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations#providenoopanimations\n - api/platform-browser/animations/provideNoopAnimations#usage-notes\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - guide/animations\n - guide/glossary#provider\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/platform-browser/animations/src/module.ts#L100-L126\n-->"}